Name: Telekinetic
About the game: Description: Telekinetic - indie horror, with not complicated puzzles, but with a mysterious story. You come to your senses in a strange place, around the damaged bodies of people and a lot of blood, you have a head pierced and, instead of the left hand, its mechanical likeness, which is endowed with an interesting feature - telekinesis. Game Features: Telekinesis - you can pick up and throw a variety of items, as well as solve some puzzles. History - your story is short, but it is covered with mystery, and it also has several possible finals. Atmosphere - immerse yourself in an atmosphere of fear and gloom.
